<div class="section" id="architecture">
<h2>1. How It Works</h2>
<p>Zero cost, fully autonomous. Here's the complete flow:</p>
<div class="step">
  <div style="font-size:12px;line-height:2.2;color:var(--text2)">
    <span style="color:var(--green)">‚ë†</span> GitHub Actions bot wakes up <strong style="color:var(--amber)">every 15 minutes</strong>, 24/7<br/>
    <span style="color:var(--green)">‚ë°</span> Fetches r/forhire + r/slavelabour via RSS (Reddit can't block this)<br/>
    <span style="color:var(--green)">‚ë¢</span> Filters out tasks AI can't do (video, design, etc.)<br/>
    <span style="color:var(--green)">‚ë£</span> Pushes doable tasks to <strong style="color:var(--amber)">Firebase</strong><br/>
    <span style="color:var(--green)">‚ë§</span> If task pays $15+, sends you a <strong style="color:var(--amber)">Gmail alert</strong><br/>
    <span style="color:var(--green)">‚ë•</span> You open dashboard on phone ‚Üí tap <strong style="color:var(--amber)">APPROVE</strong><br/>
    <span style="color:var(--green)">‚ë¶</span> Bot picks up approved task, runs it through <strong style="color:var(--amber)">Gemini AI</strong> (free)<br/>
    <span style="color:var(--green)">‚ëß</span> Completed deliverable appears in your dashboard<br/>
    <span style="color:var(--green)">‚ë®</span> You copy it ‚Üí reply to Reddit post ‚Üí client pays you<br/>
    <span style="color:var(--green)">‚ë©</span> Tap <strong style="color:var(--amber)">MARK PAID üí∞</strong> in dashboard
  </div>
</div>

<table>
  <tr><th>Component</th><th>What It Does</th><th>Cost</th></tr>
