</div>

<!-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê -->
<div class="section" id="gmail">
<h2>5. Gmail App Password</h2>
<p>Required for email alerts. Takes 2 minutes.</p>

<div class="step"><div class="step-num">STEP 1</div><br/>Go to <a class="url" href="https://myaccount.google.com/security">myaccount.google.com/security</a><br/>Make sure <strong style="color:var(--amber)">2-Step Verification is ON</strong> (required for App Passwords)</div>
<div class="step"><div class="step-num">STEP 2</div><br/>Go to <a class="url" href="https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords">myaccount.google.com/apppasswords</a></div>
<div class="step"><div class="step-num">STEP 3</div><br/>In "App name" type: <strong style="color:var(--amber)">taskforce</strong><br/>Tap <strong style="color:var(--amber)">Create</strong></div>
<div class="step"><div class="step-num">STEP 4</div><br/>Copy the 16-character code shown (e.g. <code style="color:var(--green)">abcd efgh ijkl mnop</code>)<br/>Remove the spaces when pasting into GitHub Secret</div>
<div class="step"><div class="step-num">STEP 5</div><br/>Go to GitHub Secrets ‚Üí Add <strong style="color:var(--amber)">GMAIL_USER</strong> (your Gmail) and <strong style="color:var(--amber)">GMAIL_PASS</strong> (the 16-char code)</div>

<div class="tip">‚úÖ After adding these secrets, update run-bot.yml to include GMAIL_USER and GMAIL_PASS env vars (already shown in the yml file above)</div>
</div>

<!-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê -->
<div class="section" id="workflow">
<h2>6. Daily Workflow</h2>

<table>
  <tr><th>Action</th><th>How</th><th>Time</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Check for tasks</td><td>Bot does it automatically every 15 min</td><td>0 sec</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Get alerted</td><td>Email lands in Gmail for $15+ tasks</td><td>0 sec</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Approve a task</td><td>Open dashboard ‚Üí tap APPROVE</td><td>5 sec</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Wait for AI</td><td>Bot runs within 15 min max</td><td>0-15 min</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Send deliverable</td><td>Tap COPY ‚Üí reply to Reddit post</td><td>30 sec</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Collect payment</td><td>Client sends PayPal/Wise</td><td>varies</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Record payment</td><td>Tap MARK PAID üí∞ in dashboard</td><td>2 sec</td></tr>
</table>

