  <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyBlock(this)">COPY</button>
  <pre id="msg1">Hi! I can help with this. I've already completed it ‚Äî here's a preview:

[paste first 2-3 sentences of deliverable]

Full work ready to send. Payment via PayPal/Wise first, then I'll send the complete file. 
What works for you?</pre>
