  <tr><td><span class="tag green">‚úÖ WRITING</span></td><td>Blog posts, articles, product descriptions, emails, bios, cover letters, proposals</td><td style="color:var(--green)">Excellent</td></tr>
  <tr><td><span class="tag green">‚úÖ RESEARCH</span></td><td>Summaries, market research, competitor analysis, fact-finding, data compilation</td><td style="color:var(--green)">Excellent</td></tr>
