<!-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê -->
<div class="section" id="troubleshoot">
<h2>9. Troubleshooting</h2>

<table>
  <tr><th>Problem</th><th>Fix</th></tr>
  <tr><td>No tasks showing in app</td><td>Tap REFRESH REDDIT NOW. Bot pushes tasks every 15 min.</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Bot failing in Actions</td><td>Check Actions logs. Most common: wrong secret name.</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Approved task stuck</td><td>Go to Actions ‚Üí Run workflow manually to trigger bot now.</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Firebase not connecting</td><td>Go to ‚öô Setup tab in app ‚Üí check Firebase URL is saved.</td></tr>
  <tr><td>No email alerts</td><td>Check GMAIL_USER and GMAIL_PASS secrets are set. Use App Password not real password.</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Bot runs but 0 tasks</td><td>All tasks already in Firebase. Clears over time as new posts come in.</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Output looks wrong</td><td>Check it yourself before sending. For coding tasks especially, review the code.</td></tr>
</table>

<h3>Manual trigger (force bot to run now)</h3>
<p>Go to <a class="url" href="https://github.com/nadavw9/taskforce/actions">github.com/nadavw9/taskforce/actions</a> ‚Üí TaskForce Bot ‚Üí Run workflow ‚Üí Run workflow</p>

<h3>Check Firebase directly</h3>
<p>Go to <a class="url" href="https://taskforce-2b7da-default-rtdb.firebaseio.com/tasks.json">taskforce-2b7da-default-rtdb.firebaseio.com/tasks.json</a> to see all tasks raw.</p>
</div>

